## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge recommended)
- Internet connection for live XRPL data
- Optional: Local proxy server for advanced features

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/808CryptoBeast/NaluXRP.git
cd NaluXRP

# Option 1: Open directly
# Simply open index.html in your browser

# Option 2: Use local server (recommended for full features)
# Python 3
python -m http.server 8000

# Node.js
npx http-server

# Then navigate to http://localhost:8000
```

### Optional: Proxy Server for Enhanced Features

For advanced Inspector features and token analytics:

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start proxy server
node js/proxy-server.js

# Proxy runs on http://localhost:3000
```

